en shelves and cabinets, a rectangular sink, and a large mirror. The walls are lined with white marble tiles.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-10-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-10-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-10-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-10-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/the-red-rock-house-is-an-architectural-dialogue-with-the-desert/red-rock-house-nevada-faulkner-architects-11/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-559159\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-11-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Modern concrete balcony with lounge seating, ambient lighting, and a view of a distant city skyline and waterfront at dusk.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-11-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-11-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-11-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-11-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/the-red-rock-house-is-an-architectural-dialogue-with-the-desert/red-rock-house-nevada-faulkner-architects-12/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-559160\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-12-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Modern architectural setting with a minimalist concrete wall, wooden deck, and an infinity pool reflecting the sky. A white lounge chair is placed on the deck.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-12-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-12-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-12-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-12-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-12.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe house is equipped with a range of energy-efficient systems, including a 45-kilowatt photovoltaic array that powers the home, high-efficiency glazing to reduce heat gain, and mechanical and lighting systems designed to minimize energy use. The roof, which is highly reflective, helps to mitigate the intense desert heat, while the design of the building itself maximizes natural ventilation and shading.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/the-red-rock-house-is-an-architectural-dialogue-with-the-desert/red-rock-house-nevada-faulkner-architects-13/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-559161\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-13-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"A modern exterior features a wooden deck, a reflecting pool, and concrete walls with a single narrow door. Cushions and a yo