the intense heat of the desert sun. The deck, which is screened with perforated mesh, also serves to protect the house and the cars parked below from the elements. This thoughtful integration of shading devices and natural ventilation systems ensures that the house remains cool and comfortable even during the hottest days of summer.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/the-red-rock-house-is-an-architectural-dialogue-with-the-desert/red-rock-house-nevada-faulkner-architects-17/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-559165\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-17-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A modern outdoor space with concrete walls, featuring four lounge chairs around a rectangular fire pit, illuminated by the fire\u0026#39;s glow. The sky is twilight blue.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-17-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-17-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-17-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-17-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/the-red-rock-house-is-an-architectural-dialogue-with-the-desert/red-rock-house-nevada-faulkner-architects-18/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-559166\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Red-Rock-House-Nevada-Faulkner-Architects-18-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"A modern, minimalist house with large glass walls, an open-plan living area, 